data.description: This beautifully updated property is one of a kind with many added features found on the documents tab.  This is the perfect larger home with a desirable floor plan, open kitchen family room overlooking the yard with one bedroom and full bath on main level and four additional rooms and loft upstairs, restaurants, entertainment, shopping for just about anything and minutes from highways.  Lower electric bills with owned solar panels transferring with house. Easy to maintain this clean home with Central Vacuum on both levels.  Plenty of storage with three car garage.
